::Reptilica/Repressor::

A few shots hit Reptilica in the back, the bot growling as he turns around 
and fires at Jetstorm with his rifle, firing down at Grenade with two more 
missiles.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

back. Not even noticing, Repressor fires another two missiles at Grenade.
